G(z) = \sum_{n \ge 0} g(n) z^n
\mathcal{G}
\mathcal{G} = \operatorname{S\scriptsize EQ}(\mathcal{O}) \implies G(z) = \frac{1}{1-O(z)} = \frac{1}{1-\frac{z}{1-z^2}} = \frac{1-z^2}{1-z-z^2}
