H(z) = \sum_{n \ge 0} h(n) z^n
\mathcal{H}
\mathcal{H} = \operatorname{S\scriptsize EQ}(\mathcal{C}) \implies H(z) = \frac{1}{1-C(z)} = \frac{1}{1-z-z^2}
