n \ge 0
\sum_{n \ge 0}g(n+1)z^n = \frac{G(z) - g(0)}{z} = \frac1z \left( \frac{1-z^2}{1-z-z^2} - 1\right) = \frac{1}{1-z-z^2} = H(z)
